<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="67" type="description">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="67">Culture characters.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="67">On PDA at 25 °C, colonies growing slowly and unevenly, reaching 70 mm diam. within 25 d, gradually becoming brownish dark grey in colour with scant cottony aerial mycelium, asexual morphs developed after 35 d.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
